<div class="card">
  <h2 class="card-title">Importar base (.xlsx)</h2>
  <p class="muted">
    Importa na ordem correta: Clientes → Eventos → Propostas → Pagamentos, mantendo vínculos via external_id.
  </p>

  <form class="form" method="POST" action="/importar" enctype="multipart/form-data">
    <label class="label">Arquivo (.xlsx)</label>
    <input class="input" type="file" name="file" accept=".xlsx" required />
    <button class="btn" type="submit">Importar</button>
  </form>
</div>
